{"tid":1062260,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人聽過長生學?","createTime":"2019-03-15T03:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T06:06:50.000Z","uid":81462,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ad4173e623abc63872e4400f2e2f151ef57f7aaa","tid":1062260,"uid":81462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T03:54:22.000Z","msg":"家母長期受失眠困擾<br />\n試過好多方法<br />\n中西醫氣功瑜珈都試過<br />\n都叫過佢臨訓前唔好睇劇 試下睇書<br />\n但都話無用<br />\n<br />\n最近佢有唔同朋友不約而同地上長生學嘅班<br />\n話係一次上六堂就搞掂 做完就可以唔上<br />\n上完之後身體好咗<br />\n但係一年係香港淨係開兩次班<br />\n啱啱呢次錯過咗<br />\n就諗住叫朋友幫佢調整下試下work唔work先<br />\nWork嘅話就下次報<br />\n<br />\n佢畀咗人地啲刊物我睇<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.longevitology.idv.tw/long/index.php/2014-07-28-06-32-05/200-89-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.longevitology.idv.tw%2Flong%2Findex.php%2F2014-07-28-06-32-05%2F200-89-4&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaYVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=59ec3bdf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.longevitology.idv.tw/long/index.php/2014-07-28-06-32-05/200-89-4</a><br />\n完完全全係邪教feel<br />\n而且google一search長生學<br />\n第二三個result就已經係邪教同騙人<br />\n但google完之後啲人一面倒咁讚, 無人鬧<br />\n但係咁先最恐怖<br />\n啲人洗晒腦咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/03/15/sIbwlk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F03%2F15%2FsIbwlk.jpg&h=b02726c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/03/15/ytk4ei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F03%2F15%2Fytk4ei.jpg&h=e0b8440e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27502912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D27502912&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaYVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=090bfd6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27502912</a><br />\n<br />\n再睇埋下面條link<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20180708/wg1h_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Fvan%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20180708%2Fwg1h_r.htm&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaYVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=e260837b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20180708/wg1h_r.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n我嘗試阻止佢<br />\n話佢朋友想導佢入教嘅話講咩都得<br />\n又唔知去到係咪要捐錢嗰啲<br />\n係慢慢滲資料洗人腦<br />\n而且我媽係人講咩就信<br />\n最怕佢上完返到黎俾人洗晒腦<br />\n日日好感恩咁 變埋另一個人<br />\n<br />\n但佢就駁我話上呢啲堂唔會有咩損失<br />\n而且如果幫到佢訓覺訓得好啲嘅話點解唔可以試<br />\n話我有偏見<br />\n其實佢一開始講長生學<br />\n都有講一句話係咪好似邪教<br />\n只係佢絕望到連邪教都想試<br />\n講完一大輪 佢只係話人地半年後先黎開班到時再算<br />\n點先可以叫佢唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855b63c12252e0bf2741459b357a5559647c5435","tid":1062260,"uid":81462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7871579aeec6feb76b43371e2d24f3c6a18add8f","tid":1062260,"uid":81462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc55f100180db15bf85f9c5bf2981c0aa06ece17","tid":1062260,"uid":81462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6216a34fef08c52596bd7fa11cc136f9b08c5d04","tid":1062260,"uid":14925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bbc4a2f9a47ffedf8ddd16df6edf0d26fdc89f","tid":1062260,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:26:44.000Z","msg":"長生訣"},{"pid":"321d8198a533b78fdb51ec37849e5fd20591e900","tid":1062260,"uid":110653,"like":1,"di